{"title": "We have to live with Covid-19 like it\u2019s the flu", "tags": "opinion", "timestamp": "2023-12-22", "content": "Like many human viruses that originated in animals, Sars-CoV-2 has adapted to life in humans. If it had not been adaptable, Covid-19 would already have been eliminated. We will thus have to live with Covid-19.\nLiving with Covid-19 means grappling with certain facts. For one thing, we must expect that the number of cases of respiratory infections will come in waves through the year."}